    <entry>
      <title>从负基础开始的小程序学习之路——初识js</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/17/%E4%BB%8E%E8%B4%9F%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%88%9D%E8%AF%86js/"/>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本篇将会出现以下内容：小程序、JavaScript以及一些奇怪的东西<br><a id="more"></a></p><hr><h2 id="学习一个"><a href="#学习一个" class="headerlink" title="学习一个"></a>学习一个</h2><h3 id="JavaScript语法："><a href="#JavaScript语法：" class="headerlink" title="JavaScript语法："></a>JavaScript语法：</h3><ul><li>const //定义必须初始化且不可修改的全局变量</li><li>var //定义全局变量或者函数变量</li><li><p>let //定义块级变量</p></li><li><p>一个JS文件中只可以存在一个page页面</p></li><li><p>Math.floor() //对一个数进行下舍入，即向下取整</p></li></ul><h2 id="提高水平"><a href="#提高水平" class="headerlink" title="提高水平"></a>提高水平</h2><ul><li>开发者工具出现不能输入中文的问题：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/xyyt/p/10005947.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解决方法</a><blockquote><p>经验证， ctrl(command) + shfit + w 重启下项目，是可行的，看来也只有如此了。<br>期待下个版本解决这个问题。</p></blockquote></li></ul><ul><li><p><a href="https://www.openxy.com/books/wx/02/show.html#%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E9%A1%B5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">教程</a>中部分内容不能通过编译：</p><blockquote><p>修改项目根目录下的 app.json 文件，如下：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  "pages":[</span><br><span class="line">    "pages/posts/show", // 第一行表示入口首页。原内容为pages/index/index，即原首页</span><br><span class="line">    "pages/logs/logs"</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  ...</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>保存后，立即会在预览窗口中看到刚才编写的show页面的渲染结果了</p></blockquote></li></ul><p>实际操作中，会报错<br><figure class="highlight console"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Page is not constructed because it is not found</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>初步判断是因为更改目录后index页面未被渲染，在<br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"pages"</span>:[</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"page/index/index"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"page/log/log"</span></span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>前加入新编写页面地址<br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">"pages"</span>:[</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"pages/posts/show"</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"pages/index/index"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"pages/log/log"</span></span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>即可编译通过正常显示</p><h2 id="一些弯路"><a href="#一些弯路" class="headerlink" title="一些弯路"></a>一些弯路</h2><ul><li>如何实现网页间的跳转？</li><li>如何在页面上生成卡牌图片？</li></ul><h2 id="下周目标"><a href="#下周目标" class="headerlink" title="下周目标"></a>下周目标</h2><ul><li>明确如何实现功能</li><li>简单的实现功能<ul><li>形成卡牌轮廓</li><li>可以上传图片</li></ul></li><li>继续学习js与wxml</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
